{
  "stem": "8892.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So sure enough, my father goes back to Liska-- and with the other one.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they loaded up, I think, about two or three wagons-- flour, schmaltz, smoked meat, if they find a little bit left, whatever.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And canned-- we didn't have canned goods.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we preserve it in jars.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the jar food, anything it was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then, when they brought it all in, they made, like, a community kitchen.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they rationed out the flour and things like that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And this way, they were able to do it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But the ration was so limited.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I remember that my sister was helping.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the older girls, the cousins and my mother, they all in a kitchen, trying to make soup with a little bit of vegetables, or whatever they had.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And at one point, I remember coming-- a package arrived.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they give it to us, which my uncle from Debrecen send us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they were goodies like salami, like, you know, regular [NON-ENGLISH] stuff, kolbase, but everything-- and packed.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And, of course, we didn't touch it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We just leave it there for a more-- worse time, and to be an emergency.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in a ghetto, you just-- it was like a-- where we were, it was a courtyard, like four buildings, [POINTING] here, here, here, and a courtyard.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We just gathered around, and just talked.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know-- and helping to be clean and sanitary, help everybody to wash.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And everybody had a chore what to do.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "How long were you in the ghetto for?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Four weeks.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then they started to, to deport us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, a trip to Auschwitz, the only thing I remember-- that our building, I think, was the last transport.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Was four transport going out of Ujhely.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
